---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions | NaughtyCamSpot"
  description="Terms and service conditions for NaughtyCamSpot."
  showNavigation={false}
>
  <section class="hero-shell parallax-veil">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-bl from-black/60 via-transparent to-black/70"></div>
    <div class="relative space-y-4">
      <span class="hero-tagline">Legal Notice</span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl text-white sm:text-5xl">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p class="max-w-3xl text-sm text-white/70">
        These terms govern your use of NaughtyCamSpot growth services, guided launch intake, and affiliate routing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70">
    <h2 class="text-base uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-rose-petal/70">Services</h2>
    <p>
      NaughtyCamSpot provides growth support for active cam models and a guided launch path for new models. Any paid growth work is
      governed by a separate written agreement that outlines scope, timing, and compensation.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-base uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-rose-petal/70">Account Control</h2>
    <p>
      We do not request passwords, take over platform accounts, or act as your legal agent. You maintain ownership and control of
      your accounts at all times.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-base uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-rose-petal/70">Eligibility</h2>
    <p>
      Clients must be 18+ with valid government identification and platform approval. We reserve the right to decline or discontinue
      support if brand alignment or compliance is compromised.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-base uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-rose-petal/70">Compliance</h2>
    <p>
      You are responsible for complying with platform terms, community guidelines, and all applicable local laws and regulations.
      We provide guidance but do not control or verify your platform compliance.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-base uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-rose-petal/70">Liability</h2>
    <p>
      While we provide strategic guidance, performers remain responsible for their content, platform compliance, and legal
      obligations. We do not guarantee earnings or outcomes and are not liable for lost revenue or disciplinary actions.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-base uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-rose-petal/70">Payment & Affiliates</h2>
    <p>
      Affiliate commissions and any paid service fees are documented in written agreements. Late payments may result in paused
      services until balances are cleared.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-base uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-rose-petal/70">Data Handling</h2>
    <p>
      Form submissions are protected with server-side validation and standard security controls appropriate to the intake flow in use.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-base uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-rose-petal/70">Dispute Resolution</h2>
    <p>
      Any disputes will be addressed through good-faith mediation before arbitration in the state of Florida, USA.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-base uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-rose-petal/70">Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about these terms can be sent to legal@naughtycamspot.com.
    </p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
